com.communote.server.persistence.common.messages

Class MultipleMessageKeyLocalizedMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.communote.server.persistence.common.messages.MultipleMessageKeyLocalizedMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LocalizedMessage, LocalizationChangeObservable

    public class MultipleMessageKeyLocalizedMessage
extends Object
implements LocalizedMessage, LocalizationChangeObservable
    Message that aggregates multiple LocalizedMessage and joins them on toString(Locale, Object...) using the provided seperator (default is a space " "). Important: The arguments provided to toString(Locale, Object...) are ignored! The arguments must be provided independently for each MessageKeyLocalizedMessage added.
    Author:
    Communote GmbH - http://www.communote.com/
